@startuml
title Agent Key 轮换流程（rotate-key）

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

<style>
  participant {
    Padding 28
  }
  box {
    Padding 10
  }
</style>

autonumber

actor "开发者" as Dev
participant "SDK\n(AgentInstance)" as SDK
participant "Vault\n(Transit)" as Vault
participant "Registry" as Registry

note over Dev, Registry
轮换前置条件：
• Agent 已通过 publish 在 Registry 建立 owner 绑定
• 当前 active key 私钥仍可访问（在 Vault 中）
• 新 key 私钥也已就绪（在 Vault 中）
end note

== 准备新密钥 ==

Dev -> Vault : 创建新 Transit key\nvault write -f transit/keys/agent-v2\ntype=ecdsa-p256
Vault --> Dev : 返回新 key 信息\nkid / public_key_pem
note right
新 key 私钥同样不可导出，
仅用于后续签名。
end note

== 发起轮换请求 ==

Dev -> SDK : agent.rotate_key(\n  registry_url, client_id, api_key,\n  new_signer, new_public_key_pem,\n  new_kid\n)

SDK -> SDK : 构造 new_key (AgentKey)\nkid=new_kid, alg=ES256\npublic_key_pem, status=active

== 步骤 1：新密钥证明 (New Key Proof) ==

SDK -> Vault : sign_registry_new_key_proof\n用 new_signer 签名 proof canonical
note over SDK, Vault
proof canonical string 绑定：
rotate-key-new-key-proof-v1
x-agent-id: {agent_id}
x-agent-kid: {new_kid}
new-key-fingerprint: {公钥指纹}
x-agent-timestamp: {timestamp}
x-agent-nonce: {nonce}
x-registry-client-id: {client_id}
host: {registry_host}
end note
Vault --> SDK : 返回 proof 签名\n{new_key_proof_headers}

== 步骤 2：旧密钥签名完整请求 ==

SDK -> Vault : sign_registry_publish_request\n用当前 active key (旧 signer)\n签名整个 rotate payload
note over SDK, Vault
publish canonical string 绑定：
method: POST
path: /registry/agents/rotate-key
body-digest: SHA-256(payload)
x-agent-id / x-agent-kid (旧)
x-agent-timestamp / x-agent-nonce
x-registry-client-id / host
end note
Vault --> SDK : 返回旧 key 签名\n{x-agent-* headers}

== 步骤 3：发送轮换请求 ==

SDK -> Registry : POST /registry/agents/rotate-key\nAuthorization: Bearer {api_key}\n旧 key 签名 headers\npayload: {agent_id, new_key,\n         new_key_proof_headers}

Registry -> Registry : 1. 校验 developer API key
Registry -> Registry : 2. 校验旧 active key 签名\n(证明旧 key 私钥仍可控)
Registry -> Registry : 3. 校验新 key proof 签名\n(证明新 key 私钥可控)
Registry -> Registry : 4. 校验 agent_id -> developer_id\nowner 匹配
Registry -> Registry : 5. 校验 timestamp 在允许偏移内
Registry -> Registry : 6. 校验 nonce 未重放

alt 全部校验通过
    Registry -> Registry : 旧 key status → inactive\n新 key status → active\n写入 registry storage
    Registry --> SDK : 200 OK\n轮换成功

    SDK -> SDK : 更新本地 AgentInstance：\n• kid = new_kid\n• public_key_pem = new_public_key_pem\n• signer_override = new_signer\n• metadata 中旧 key 标为 inactive
    SDK --> Dev : 返回成功响应

else 任一校验失败
    Registry --> SDK : 4xx / 5xx 拒绝轮换
    note over SDK, Registry
      常见拒绝 detail：
      • INVALID_API_KEY — developer 凭证无效
      • SIGNATURE_INVALID — 旧 key 签名无效
      • NEW_KEY_PROOF_INVALID — 新 key proof 无效
      • OWNER_MISMATCH — 非本 Agent 的 owner
      • TIMESTAMP_EXPIRED — 请求过期
      • NONCE_REPLAYED — nonce 重放
    end note
    SDK --> Dev : 抛出 httpx.HTTPStatusError\n本地状态不变
end

note over Dev, Registry
轮换安全保证：
1. 双签名证明：旧 key + 新 key 私钥均需可控
2. 任一 key 私钥泄露无法单独完成轮换
3. owner 绑定防止他人轮换你的 Agent key
4. timestamp + nonce 防止重放攻击
end note

@enduml
